The GNU Wireless Network project README file



=== GWN environment variables

--- Adjust PYTHONPATH variable for GWN imports
Add the following lines to your .bashrc file:

   # GWN path
   PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:<your_GWN_install_dir>/gwn
   export PYTHONPATH

Then do
    source .bashrc

Finally try
    python
    >>> import blocks.framers.ieee80211
Should do with no errors.

WARNING: to test modules which require 'sudo', you must do
  sudo env PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:<your_GWN_install_dir>/gwn python tuntap.py 
since 'sudo python' does not see PYTHONPATH user variable.


=== The GWN Library structure
State: in progress.


Upper level:
  Files:
    COPYING : text of the the GPL license.
    README : this file.
    README.md : a project description required by Github.

  Main directories:
    doc : public documentation; style guide, extension manuals.
    draft : for developers.
    gwn : code root directory.

gwn subdirectories:

  - blocks
      - framers
          - ieee80211 : framer, deframer blocks for IEEE 802.11 frames
          - strframes : framer, deframer blocks for string frames (not yet)
      - libio
          - gnuradio
            uhd_interface.py:               ### from GNU radio
            TxRxLayer1.py:                  ### from GNU radio
            transmit_path.py:               ### from GNU radio
            transmit_path3_7.py:            ### from GNU radio
            receive_path.py:                ### from GNU radio
            receive_path3_7.py:             ### from GNU radio
            psk.py                          ### 2014-07-28 all tests pass
          - tuntap                          ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
      - mac
          - generic_fdma <-- libMAC
          - generic_tdma <-- libmacTDMA
          - ieee80211 <-- libmac80211
      - management <-- libmanagement
            - ieee80211 : beacon, discovery and peering (to rebuild)
      - simulators <-- libvirtualchannel    ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
            - generators                    ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
            - consumers                     ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
            - channels                      ### no tests
      - utilblocks
          - classifiers (empty for now)
          - schedulers  (empty for now)
          - timer <-- libtimer              ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass

  - epydoc_doc  <-- doc : how to write docstrings for the Epydoc documentation program.

  - gwnblocks : the abstract classes, tests.     ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
          - gwntimer --> gwnintimer

  - gwnc <-- grc : the GWN Companion.

  - gwnevents : events, structure under design.

  - html : the Epydoc generated code documentation.

  - logs : log files generated by the GWN logger.

  - scripts : the grc scripts, for the GWN Companion.
        gwnblock_test_stress.py (tests how many threads can be created)
        top_block.py                            ### generated
        gnuradio_test.grc
        gnuradio_test_simulator.grc
        gnu_winet.grc
        test_FDMA.grc                           ### 2014-07-17 script working
        test_framer_deframer_80211.grc          ### 2014-07-17 script working
        test_simulator_consumer.grc             ### 2014-07-17 script working
        test_simulator_consumer_timer.grc       ### 2014-07-17 script working
        test_simulator_consumer_with_loss.grc   ### 2014-07-17 script working
        test_tuntap.grc                         ### 2014-07-17 script working

  - utils <-- libutils
        - framers
            - ieee80211 <-- libframes           ### 2014-07-17 all tests pass
            - strframes (not yet)
        - libfsm : Finite State Machines.
        - logger : the GWN logger facility.
        - testing : test code.

  - xml : block descriptions for the GWN Companion
        80211DeFramer.xml                       ### 2014-07-17 block working
        80211Framer.xml                         ### 2014-07-17 block working
        EventConsumer.xml                       ### 2014-07-17 block working
        EventSimulator.xml                      ### 2014-07-17 block working
        evtype_clasifier.xml
        fdma.xml                                ### 2014-07-17 block working
        gnuradio-grc.desktop
        gnuradiopsk.xml
        options.xml                             ### 2014-07-17 block working
        parameter.xml                           ### 2014-07-17 block working
        timer.xml                               ### 2014-07-17 block working
        TunTapInterface.xml                     ### 2014-07-17 block working
        variable.xml                            ### 2014-07-17 block working
        virtualchannel.xml                      ### 2014-07-17 block working


